00:30.051 --> 00:33.675
But instead, the discriminators, they operate on very small windows.

00:34.136 --> 00:42.205
So in specific, they have five different discriminators, and each of the five different discriminators take a different size window length.

00:42.225 --> 00:44.187
But all of these windows are super short.

00:44.287 --> 00:48.972
So one discriminator might take this long windows.

00:48.952 --> 00:54.901
